msgstr "Je kunt de volledige sleutel vinden onder Instellingen → API-Keys in je Deepglot project."

#: includes/Admin/SettingsPage.php:244
msgid "Backend-URL"
msgstr "Backend URL"

#: includes/Admin/SettingsPage.php:252
msgid "Standard: https://deepglot.ai/api – nur ändern bei Self-Hosting."
msgstr "Standaard: https://deepglot.ai/api – alleen wijziging voor Self-Hosting."

#: includes/Admin/SettingsPage.php:264
msgid "Sprachen konfigurieren"
